Marks Brothers retains advertising firm . Marks Bros . Jewelers Inc said Friday it retained Barkley & Evergreen , a full - service advertising and marketing firm . Barkley & Evergreen will provide full - service marketing communications , including strategic planning , media planning , advertising , database marketing and direct mail , and customer service consulting , it said . " Historically , we have not engaged in a formal marketing effort , but we believe that as the jewelry retail industry continues to consolidate , it is important to build our brand awareness , " Hugh Patinkin , chairman , said in a statement . Marks Bros . is a national specialty retailer of fine jewelry , operating 179 stores in 24 states . ( ( Reuters Chicago Newsdesk ( 312 ) 408 - 8787 ) ) 
